title: AIM on DS
description:
This is a .nds file for nintendo ds. It uses the nintendo ds wifi. Very simple usage and its nice to not have to have AIM open on the computer =p

Simply run the file from your ds, and enter your username. then press down on the virtual keyboard and enter your password. then press send to sign in.

To IM someone, press either L or R and select the contact with the stylus. Then press IM on the bottom of the screen.

Very simple ^.-
